Staircase detection sw description

-stair_detection_ros.cpp  : main function call for staircase detection including SVM classifier and rule-base classifier

- stair_detec_only_rgb.cpp : sub-function using only RGB image

- stair_detec_pre_proc.cpp : line extraction

- stiar_detec_cost_func.cpp : calculate three factors




- util/correlation_sampe_with_svm_ros.cpp : extract the sample points in the true label set of SVM

- util/svm_training_ros.cpp : offline svm training using training set

- util/svm_trainingset_genfromdir_ros.cpp : 
